    "prompt": "A conceptual illustration of interdisciplinary integration, featuring interconnected gears of different sizes and colors representing distinct academic fields like materials science, artificial intelligence, and systems engineering, seamlessly meshing together to form a complex, functional mechanism, symbolizing knowledge fusion and collaborative problem-solving.",
